FT  03 DEC 94 / UK Company News: B Elliott expands
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
B Elliott, the specialist engineer, is buying Flight Link Control and Crane
Control Systems for a maximum Pounds 1.1m.
In addition, it is contributing Pounds 600,000 to a joint venture with Ohta
Press of Japan to manufacture its range for the European market.
It is also setting up a 55 per cent joint venture in China to make its
measurement and digital read-out systems.
