</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By REUTER
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   NICOSIA
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Turkish Cypriot authorities have obtained a court order against a bank owned
by fugitive tycoon Mr Asil Nadir for defaulting on Dollars 4.2m in deposits
for a pension fund, Mr Ozkan Murat, minister of labour and social security,
said on Thursday. 'We have taken legal action to make sure this money is not
