trying to rally support for a separate offer.
Their advisers say the traders have the backing of CSN, the Brazilian steel
producer. They have also been seeking to add Usinor Sacilor of France and
Lucchini, the private Italian steel manufacturer, to the consortium, and
could make a formal offer next week.
