    FRZ  France, EC.
    GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
    IEZ  Ireland, EC.
    QRZ  European Economic Community (EC).
    PTZ  Portugal, EC.
    NLZ  Netherlands, EC.
    DKZ  Denmark, EC.
    INZ  India, Asia.
</CN>
