FT  02 DEC 94 / World News in Brief: Manila ferry sinks
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A ferry carrying 488 people collided with a cargo ship and sank off Manila.
At least 275 people were rescued and ships were still picking up survivors
early today.
